steps.prompt:
Analyze this feature brainstorm:

{{TRANSCRIPT}}

Extract distinct feature ideas and evaluate each. Return JSON:
{
  "project": "project name if mentioned, else 'General'",
  "features": [
    {
      "title": "short feature title",
      "description": "1-2 sentence description",
      "impact": "high|medium|low",
      "effort": "high|medium|low",
      "category": "ux|performance|integration|infrastructure|polish",
      "dependencies": ["other features or prerequisites if any"]
    }
  ],
  "quickWins": ["features that are high impact + low effort"],
  "bigBets": ["features that are high impact + high effort"],
  "contextNotes": "any important context or constraints mentioned"
}

steps.content:
---
created: {{DATE}}
project: "{{parsed.project}}"
type: feature-ideation
---

# Feature Ideas: {{parsed.project}}

{{formatted}}

---

## Raw Brainstorm

> {{TRANSCRIPT}}
